1
00:00:02,887 --> 00:00:07,899
♪Do you know, our fingertips
are bound by one string♪

2
00:00:07,900 --> 00:00:12,499
♪Tied to an attachment
that blooms only to fade♪

3
00:00:12,500 --> 00:00:13,999
♪By your side once♪

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:17,074
♪I laughed with the world
wild and free♪

5
00:00:17,075 --> 00:00:21,049
♪Yet now there's no one
to carry the story on♪

6
00:00:21,050 --> 00:00:25,970
♪Do you know you are the one string
woven through my fate♪

7
00:00:25,987 --> 00:00:30,699
♪Coiled through the years,
where longing sharpens into pain's line♪

8
00:00:30,700 --> 00:00:35,261
♪If love is meant to fall
more wretched the fiercer its flight♪

9
00:00:35,262 --> 00:00:40,445
♪Yet I still came to answer your call♪

10
00:00:40,725 --> 00:00:43,086
=Shall We Dance=

11
00:00:43,087 --> 00:00:46,120
=Episode 14=

12
00:00:46,620 --> 00:00:49,380
However, I no longer want his life.

13
00:00:51,860 --> 00:00:53,580
What I want...

14
00:00:55,300 --> 00:00:58,500
is to seize the throne!

15
00:01:06,540 --> 00:01:07,820
You're still young.

16
00:01:08,687 --> 00:01:11,887
If one day you experience

17
00:01:12,220 --> 00:01:15,220
the person who led you out of darkness

18
00:01:15,800 --> 00:01:17,499
dying before your eyes,

19
00:01:17,500 --> 00:01:19,940
while you're powerless to stop it...

20
00:01:22,300 --> 00:01:25,740
then you'll understand
the hatred in my heart.

21
00:01:28,500 --> 00:01:31,060
(30 years ago, 2nd Year of Chengshun Reign)
My mother is already dead.

22
00:01:31,140 --> 00:01:33,780
I have no money to repay you.

23
00:01:33,820 --> 00:01:36,939
(Xiao Bao, Young Jia Yi)
Wait until I've buried my mother.

24
00:01:36,940 --> 00:01:39,795
Then you can sell me, alright?

25
00:01:39,796 --> 00:01:41,419
(Zhen Xiujin, Xiao Congrong)

26
00:01:41,420 --> 00:01:42,820
Otherwise...

27
00:01:43,220 --> 00:01:44,819
if my mother sees me

28
00:01:44,820 --> 00:01:46,619
being sold off like this,

29
00:01:46,620 --> 00:01:48,460
she'll be heartbroken.

30
00:01:49,780 --> 00:01:51,300
What's your name?

31
00:01:52,260 --> 00:01:53,699
They say

32
00:01:53,700 --> 00:01:55,659
I'm an illegitimate child,

33
00:01:55,660 --> 00:01:57,180
a cursed child.

34
00:01:57,540 --> 00:02:00,219
So I don't deserve a name.

35
00:02:00,220 --> 00:02:01,699
(Before Father died,)

36
00:02:01,700 --> 00:02:03,220
he told me I had a younger brother.

37
00:02:03,260 --> 00:02:05,380
We're half-brothers of the same father.

38
00:02:05,860 --> 00:02:07,660
Now, I've found you.

39
00:02:08,140 --> 00:02:10,100
You're my real younger brother.

40
00:02:11,740 --> 00:02:13,179
I have a family now.

41
00:02:13,180 --> 00:02:15,060
I have family at last.

42
00:02:15,220 --> 00:02:17,300
Will I get a name too?

43
00:02:17,340 --> 00:02:18,620
Be good, Xiao Bao.

44
00:02:18,740 --> 00:02:20,740
Let me give you one, alright?

45
00:02:21,740 --> 00:02:24,180
Your brother is named Zhen Xiujin.

46
00:02:24,500 --> 00:02:26,500
So you'll be Zhen Xiuyi.

47
00:02:27,140 --> 00:02:30,100
May you grow up content and at peace.

48
00:02:35,262 --> 00:02:35,819
Don't cry.

49
00:02:35,820 --> 00:02:38,380
(When the whole world had abandoned me,)

50
00:02:39,820 --> 00:02:42,380
(my brother
and sister-in-law gave me a name.)

51
00:02:43,140 --> 00:02:44,820
(I found myself.)

52
00:02:45,380 --> 00:02:47,900
(I gained a home in the truest sense.)

53
00:02:48,724 --> 00:02:50,339
(Zhen Residence)

54
00:02:50,340 --> 00:02:52,560
(20 years ago, 12th Year of Chengshun Reign)
But then...

55
00:03:05,820 --> 00:03:07,780
Xiao Congrong, receive the decree.

56
00:03:10,620 --> 00:03:12,019
By the Mandate of Heaven,

57
00:03:12,020 --> 00:03:13,500
His Majesty decrees.

58
00:03:14,020 --> 00:03:14,979
Xiao Congrong,

59
00:03:14,980 --> 00:03:17,780
Zhen Xiujin and his wife have
colluded with the enemy.

60
00:03:18,180 --> 00:03:21,180
You are ordered to surrender
your military command

61
00:03:21,380 --> 00:03:23,340
and await punishment.

62
00:03:24,140 --> 00:03:25,300
Impossible.

63
00:03:25,420 --> 00:03:27,740
The Zhen clan has always been loyal.

64
00:03:27,780 --> 00:03:29,699
Someone must be
scheming and sowing discord

65
00:03:29,700 --> 00:03:31,500
between Xiujin and His Majesty.

66
00:03:31,820 --> 00:03:32,980
Easy there.

67
00:03:33,060 --> 00:03:35,699
His Majesty has a second decree.

68
00:03:35,700 --> 00:03:36,739
He says that

69
00:03:36,740 --> 00:03:38,939
if General Xiao refuses
to obey the decree,

70
00:03:38,940 --> 00:03:40,420
it will be deemed rebellion.

71
00:03:40,820 --> 00:03:43,140
And the hundred thousand Xiao troops

72
00:03:43,420 --> 00:03:45,499
will be executed alongside you.

73
00:03:45,500 --> 00:03:46,739
I don't believe it.

74
00:03:46,740 --> 00:03:48,700
I want to see the decree myself.

75
00:03:51,020 --> 00:03:52,619
What I say

76
00:03:52,620 --> 00:03:54,340
is the decree.

77
00:03:58,940 --> 00:04:00,260
Xiao Congrong,

78
00:04:00,420 --> 00:04:01,379
have you not wondered

79
00:04:01,380 --> 00:04:03,780
how I obtained the decree?

80
00:04:04,700 --> 00:04:07,740
The Xiao Army is already
surrounded at the frontier.

81
00:04:07,887 --> 00:04:09,979
Will you die alone,

82
00:04:09,980 --> 00:04:12,940
or drag your troops
to their graves with you?

83
00:04:13,180 --> 00:04:14,980
Think carefully.

84
00:04:15,420 --> 00:04:17,540
Despicable eunuch.

85
00:04:18,100 --> 00:04:20,340
Xiao Congrong defies
the imperial decree.

86
00:04:20,700 --> 00:04:22,700
Execute her now!

87
00:04:28,780 --> 00:04:30,019
You fools.

88
00:04:30,020 --> 00:04:31,059
What are you afraid of?

89
00:04:31,060 --> 00:04:32,636
Whoever kills her

90
00:04:32,637 --> 00:04:34,757
will be rewarded with rank and title.

91
00:04:35,340 --> 00:04:36,179
General Xiao

92
00:04:36,180 --> 00:04:38,100
is no easy opponent for us.

93
00:04:38,180 --> 00:04:39,407
Useless lot!

94
00:04:41,060 --> 00:04:42,260
You, the new guy.

95
00:04:42,900 --> 00:04:43,499
Come here.

96
00:04:43,500 --> 00:04:45,260
(I heard the Zhen family was in danger,)

97
00:04:45,860 --> 00:04:47,580
(so I infiltrated
the Embroidered Guards,)

98
00:04:48,020 --> 00:04:51,380
(ready to die to save
my brother and his wife.)

99
00:05:33,820 --> 00:05:34,699
If I don't die today,

100
00:05:34,700 --> 00:05:37,020
more people will be implicated.

101
00:05:37,380 --> 00:05:38,580
Listen to me.

102
00:05:38,620 --> 00:05:40,059
Don't act rashly.

103
00:05:40,060 --> 00:05:41,580
Save yourself.

104
00:05:41,820 --> 00:05:43,900
The two children are
in the hidden chamber.

105
00:05:43,940 --> 00:05:45,900
I entrust them to you.

106
00:05:46,180 --> 00:05:48,180
I won't say this twice.

107
00:06:17,940 --> 00:06:19,100
(From that day forward,)

108
00:06:19,580 --> 00:06:21,579
(there is no more
Zhen Xiuyi in this world.)

109
00:06:21,580 --> 00:06:24,619
(There is only Jia Yi,
who lives for revenge.)

110
00:06:24,620 --> 00:06:25,819
Jia Yi.

111
00:06:25,820 --> 00:06:26,940
Yes.

112
00:06:27,900 --> 00:06:30,100
You've come of age.

113
00:06:30,380 --> 00:06:33,140
The risks of castration
to enter the palace are great.

114
00:06:33,500 --> 00:06:34,939
Can you accept them?

115
00:06:34,940 --> 00:06:36,540
You needn't worry, sir.

116
00:06:37,060 --> 00:06:38,620
Why is that?

117
00:06:45,020 --> 00:06:46,620
What is this?

118
00:06:47,020 --> 00:06:49,419
I've already castrated myself.

119
00:06:49,420 --> 00:06:51,259
These are the instruments used.

120
00:06:51,260 --> 00:06:53,940
You may verify it at any time, sir.

121
00:06:55,300 --> 00:06:56,419
Godfather,

122
00:06:56,420 --> 00:06:57,699
from this day on,

123
00:06:57,700 --> 00:06:59,940
I ask for your guidance
toward honour and fortune.

124
00:07:02,220 --> 00:07:03,580
You've shown resolve.

125
00:07:04,740 --> 00:07:05,860
Come, then.

126
00:07:25,564 --> 00:07:29,480
(10 years ago,
22nd Year of Chengshun Reign)

127
00:07:47,220 --> 00:07:48,619
The Crown Prince is coughing.

128
00:07:48,620 --> 00:07:51,780
Consort Sheng has
sent over tremella porridge.

129
00:07:52,100 --> 00:07:52,539
Good.

130
00:07:52,540 --> 00:07:53,820
It'll soothe the throat.

131
00:07:55,660 --> 00:07:56,139
Wait.

132
00:07:56,140 --> 00:07:57,380
Your Highness,

133
00:07:57,500 --> 00:07:59,940
allow me to  taste it first.

134
00:08:01,020 --> 00:08:02,219
From now on,

135
00:08:02,220 --> 00:08:04,499
anything that passes
Your Highness's lips

136
00:08:04,500 --> 00:08:06,500
must be tested by me first.

137
00:08:12,060 --> 00:08:13,139
Jia Yi!

138
00:08:13,140 --> 00:08:14,260
Jia Yi!

139
00:08:15,940 --> 00:08:16,699
I'm sorry.

140
00:08:16,700 --> 00:08:19,100
I didn't know it would harm you.

141
00:08:20,660 --> 00:08:22,099
Don't move.

142
00:08:22,100 --> 00:08:23,419
Listen to me.

143
00:08:23,420 --> 00:08:26,499
You ended up like this because of me.

144
00:08:26,500 --> 00:08:28,699
Father said that if you recover,

145
00:08:28,700 --> 00:08:31,380
he'll appoint you Chief Eunuch.

146
00:08:34,820 --> 00:08:38,259
Mother once told me
carp bring good fortune.

147
00:08:38,260 --> 00:08:40,340
I folded one for you.

148
00:08:40,700 --> 00:08:43,139
It'll bless you with a swift recovery

149
00:08:43,140 --> 00:08:45,779
and restore your beautiful voice.

150
00:08:45,780 --> 00:08:46,619
Jia Yi,

151
00:08:46,620 --> 00:08:50,060
I'll hum you a tune Mother taught me.

152
00:08:50,260 --> 00:08:53,340
You'll feel better once you hear it.

153
00:09:15,980 --> 00:09:17,339
I should go now.

154
00:09:17,340 --> 00:09:19,260
Rest well.

155
00:09:43,980 --> 00:09:45,300
(Xiujin, Congrong...)

156
00:09:46,900 --> 00:09:49,660
(I endured humiliation for six years.)

157
00:09:50,860 --> 00:09:54,060
(I've finally gained a chance
to get close to the young emperor.)

158
00:10:21,100 --> 00:10:24,220
(I swear
I'll make sure those who harmed you...)

159
00:10:25,140 --> 00:10:25,899
(are...)

160
00:10:25,900 --> 00:10:26,339
(torn...)

161
00:10:26,340 --> 00:10:27,139
(into...)

162
00:10:27,140 --> 00:10:28,220
(a thousand pieces.)
